commit_message:
Change ''' to """ in bin/nova-{novncproxy,spicehtml5proxy}

Standard practice is for doc comment strings to be enclosed
in """ rather than '''. bin/nova-{novncproxy,spicehtml5proxy}
were exceptions to this.

